OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773027580
OL,3,CDemonstrators gather outside Iranian
OL,4,Cembassy in support of war
OL,6,FAround 200 demonstrators gathered
OL,7,Foutside the Iranian embassy in central
OL,8,FLondon to show their support for the
OL,9,FUS and Israeli strikes on Iran.
OL,11,FThe demonstrators stood behind
OL,12,Fbarriers across the road from the
OL,13,Fembassy next to Hyde Park on Sunday
OL,14,Fafternoon, shouting "shame on you,
OL,15,Fshame on you".
OL,17,FMany waved old Iranian flags, which
OL,18,Fwere replaced after the Iranian
OL,19,Frevolution, featuring a lion and a sun
OL,20,Frepresenting ancient Iranian history
OL,21,Fand royalty.
OL,26,@vD@UOUwD@MO]
