OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1773027580
OL,3,CDemonstrators gather outside Iranian
OL,4,Cembassy in support of war
OL,6,FOthers held US and Israeli flags, and
OL,7,Fportraits of US President Donald Trump
OL,8,Fand Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin
OL,9,FNetanyahu which read "We Trust You".
OL,11,FSeveral protesters were holding
OL,12,Fpictures of Iran's Supreme Leader
OL,13,FAyatollah Ali Khamenei, who was killed
OL,14,Fin the war's opening air strikes last
OL,15,FSaturday.
OL,17,FParisa Ashkboos, 47, and her mother
OL,18,FZari, 67, who are Iranian, travelled
OL,19,Ffrom Leicester on Sunday to attend the
OL,20,Fdemonstration.
OL,26,@qD@VOUqD@cO]
