OL,3,CDemonstrators gather outside Iranian
OL,4,Cembassy in support of war
OL,6,FHolding a former Iranian flag and an
OL,7,FIsraeli flag, Parisa Ashkboos said:
OL,8,F"We want the world to hear us and see
OL,9,Fwe are with the war, and we know this
OL,10,Fwar is good for us."
OL,12,FSpeaking of the Iranian government,
OL,13,Fshe said: "The regime is a terrorist
OL,14,Fregime."
OL,16,FMs Ashkboos added: "Thankfully, Israel
OL,17,Fand America decided to help us, to be
OL,18,Four saviour, and we are so thankful to
OL,19,Fthem.
