OL,3,CDemonstrators gather outside Iranian
OL,4,Cembassy in support of war
OL,6,F"We are delighted that somebody
OL,7,Fdecided to do something, because we
OL,8,Fjust couldn't give more death. We just
OL,9,Fcouldn't."
OL,11,FDozens of cars and motorcycles
OL,12,Fdecorated with old Iranian flags drove
OL,13,Fpast the protesters outside the
OL,14,Fembassy throughout the afternoon,
OL,15,Froaring their engines and honking
OL,16,Ftheir horns.
