OL,3,CDemonstrators gather outside Iranian
OL,4,Cembassy in support of war
OL,6,FSoby Amiri, 37, who attended the
OL,7,Fdemonstration with his family, said
OL,8,Fthe death of the late ayatollah was
OL,9,F"the price you have to pay for
OL,10,Ffreedom".
OL,12,FHe said: "Me and all my family decided
OL,13,Fto come to show our presence and
OL,14,Fsupport.
OL,16,F"So maybe the UK government can
OL,17,Frecognise that actually most Iranians
OL,18,Fare very happy and supportful of
OL,19,Fwhat's happening in Iran right now.
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@HO]tD@JOUxD@AOU
