OL,3,CDemonstrators gather outside Iranian
OL,4,Cembassy in support of war
OL,6,F"Unfortunately, blood has been shed,
OL,7,Fbut this government will now live
OL,8,Fwithout killing more innocent people.
OL,10,F"This is the price you have to pay for
OL,11,Ffreedom."
OL,13,FReyhan Sadeghi, 61, said she was "so
OL,14,Fthankful to the US and Israel" for the
OL,15,Fstrikes on Iran.
OL,17,FHolding a picture of Mr Trump and Mr
OL,18,FNetanyahu, she said: "We are so happy.
