OL,3,CDemonstrators gather outside Iranian
OL,4,Cembassy in support of war
OL,6,F"We are thankful to the US and Israel,
OL,7,Ffor fighting for us, for helping us.
OL,8,FBecause they are."
OL,10,FAsked about the death of the late
OL,11,Fayatollah, she said: "We are happy. We
OL,12,Fare over the moon, and we are dancing."
OL,14,FPointing at the Iranian embassy across
OL,15,Fthe road, she added: "This is the
OL,16,Fembassy of the Islamic Republic."
