OL,3,CDemonstrators gather outside Iranian
OL,4,Cembassy in support of war
OL,6,FDozens of police officers were present
OL,7,Fat the protest and around the Iranian
OL,8,Fembassy on Sunday afternoon, after the
OL,9,FMetropolitan Police said it had
OL,10,Fstepped up patrols across London ahead
OL,11,Fof several demonstrations and
OL,12,Fgatherings over the weekend.
OL,14,FOutside the embassy, protesters
OL,15,Fcheered and applauded as people
OL,16,Fmarching with The Lion Guard of Iran
OL,17,Fwalked past on their way to the
OL,18,FIsraeli embassy a few streets away.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
