OL,3,CDemonstrators gather outside Iranian
OL,4,Cembassy in support of war
OL,6,FProtesters dispersed around 5.30pm,
OL,7,Fafter conditions were put in place by
OL,8,Fthe Metropolitan Police earlier on
OL,9,FSunday.
